window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p> During a train trip from Chicago to Texas in the late 1940s, A.W. Tozer began to write <i>The Pursuit of God</i>. He wrote all night, and when the train arrived at his destination, the rough draft was done. The depth of this book has made it an enduring favorite.</p>"; 
